  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375\t0C (200\u0000\u001382F).",
    "Line a baking sheet with parchment paper.",
    "Cut the ssam-wrap in half lengthwise and place on the baking sheet.",
    "Spread 2 tablespoons of melted butter on each half of the wrap.",
    "Top each half with 1/6 of the Vialone-Nano Rice, 1/6 of the Crispy Bacon, 1/6 of the Red Onion, and 1/6 of the Fresh Chives.",
    "Fold the ssam-wrap in half to enclose the filling and press the edges to seal.",
    "Bake for 10-15 minutes, or until the wrap is crispy and golden brown.",
    "Repeat with the remaining ingredients.",
    "Serve warm, with additional butter if desired.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh chives, if desired."
